[SPEAKER_24]: It has changed hands a few times and I think it's currently that.

337
00:36:27,361 --> 00:36:32,504
[SPEAKER_24]: And then a parking lot, a small apartment building and then some small multifamilies next to it.

338
00:36:33,815 --> 00:36:34,515
[SPEAKER_24]: That's the B.A.

339
