01:35:34,064 --> 01:35:34,384
[SPEAKER_20]: Thank you.

1007
01:35:34,424 --> 01:35:48,508
[SPEAKER_20]: Just to confirm again, I had removed walking court from BA3, no parking mandate for the lodgers, allow purpose-built student housing use, and generally supportive of the currently proposed heights.

1008
01:35:49,848 --> 01:35:50,188
[SPEAKER_07]: That's correct.

1009
