1025
01:36:13,230 --> 01:36:17,331
[SPEAKER_22]: Thank you, everyone, for being here, and good to see everybody again, a few nights in a row.

1026
01:36:18,391 --> 01:36:20,531
[SPEAKER_22]: So I'm excited to hear about Wackling Court.

1027
