1783
02:46:49,555 --> 02:46:52,896
[SPEAKER_09]: So does that count for disqualification?

1784
02:46:53,597 --> 02:46:59,159
[SPEAKER_09]: If you can't do it for a house, does it count it's across the street?

1785
02:46:59,959 --> 02:47:06,361
[SPEAKER_09]: But basically, I'm opposed to any kind of zoning that would allow a 600-bed student housing on that corner.

1786
