1805
02:47:59,708 --> 02:48:01,410
[SPEAKER_15]: And I got to attend Monday's meeting.

1806
02:48:01,450 --> 02:48:03,611
[SPEAKER_15]: And I'm here now because I care that much.

1807
02:48:03,751 --> 02:48:05,893
