[SPEAKER_20]: Yes, iPhone 39, if you could change your name or start your video so that we know that you are a real person.

2184
03:22:01,576 --> 03:22:04,457
[SPEAKER_20]: We have been burned in the past.

2185
03:22:11,720 --> 03:22:13,021
[SPEAKER_20]: iPhone 39.

2186
03:22:15,002 --> 03:22:16,783
[SPEAKER_20]: Oh, their hand went down, okay.

