03:22:18,607 --> 03:22:22,610
[SPEAKER_07]: All right, I think with that.

2188
03:22:22,630 --> 03:22:23,991
[SPEAKER_20]: Oh, we've got one person.

2189
03:22:24,011 --> 03:22:27,774
[SPEAKER_20]: Nope, we've got one person.

2190
03:22:27,874 --> 03:22:30,255
[SPEAKER_20]: Oh, iPhone 39 now has started their video.

2191
03:22:30,396 --> 03:22:33,678
[SPEAKER_20]: So I'm going to, I see that they are a human being.

2192
03:22:33,698 --> 03:22:35,079
[SPEAKER_20]: I will unmute them.

2193
